OL,3,CCardiff to host Community Shield match
OL,4,Cafter Wembley date clash
OL,6,FThis year's FA Community Shield match
OL,7,Fwill be held at the Principality
OL,8,FStadium, it has been announced.
OL,10,FThe game, which sees the winning team
OL,11,Fof the Premier League and the winners
OL,12,Fof the FA Cup play one another, is
OL,13,Fusually held at Wembley Stadium.
OL,15,FHowever the London venue is already
OL,16,Fbooked for a concert on Sunday 16
OL,17,FAugust, so the game will be hosted in
OL,18,FCardiff on that date instead.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/5
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
