PN,46402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1774372288
OL,3,CCardiff to host Community Shield match
OL,4,Cafter Wembley date clash
OL,6,FIt is the first time in 20 years the
OL,7,FCommunity Shield has been held in
OL,8,FCardiff.
OL,10,FWith the Premier League season set to
OL,11,Fbegin over the weekend of Saturday 22
OL,12,FAugust, the Community Shield game will
OL,13,Fbe played ahead of that season kicking
OL,14,Foff.
OL,16,FThe Principality Stadium has staged
OL,17,Fthe Community Shield on six occasions
OL,18,Fbetween 2001 and 2006.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/5
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,465,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1774372288
OL,3,CCardiff to host Community Shield match
OL,4,Cafter Wembley date clash
OL,6,FGavin Marshall, Chief Financial and
OL,7,FOperating Officer at the WRU, who
OL,8,Foperate the stadium said they were
OL,9,F"delighted" that the game was
OL,10,Freturning to Cardiff.
OL,12,FHe said: "We are absolutely delighted
OL,13,Fto be welcoming the FA Community
OL,14,FShield back to Principality Stadium.
OL,15,FThis fixture has a special place in
OL,16,Fthe stadium's history and to be
OL,17,Fhosting it again for the first time in
OL,18,F20 years is a tremendously proud
OL,19,Fmoment for everyone here.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/5
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,465,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1774372288
OL,3,CCardiff to host Community Shield match
OL,4,Cafter Wembley date clash
OL,6,F"Principality Stadium has built its
OL,7,Freputation on delivering world-class
OL,8,Fevents and creating truly special
OL,9,Foccasions for fans, and this is no
OL,10,Fdifferent. We know from experience the
OL,11,Fatmosphere this stadium generates when
OL,12,Fit is at capacity, and we are fully
OL,13,Fcommitted to ensuring supporters of
OL,14,Fboth clubs have an unforgettable
OL,15,Fexperience on 16 August. This is
OL,16,Fexactly the kind of occasion this
OL,17,Fstadium was made for, and we cannot
OL,18,Fwait to welcome everyone to Cardiff."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/5
